data.text:
Photograph of movie people promoting their films in Helsinki: Jean Aurel (to the left), Lasse Mårtenson, Kristiina Halkola, Titta Karakorpi, and Lars Åberg.

Lasse Mårtenson after winning the Finnish national final for the Eurovision Song Contest 1964 with the song "Laiskotellen", showing his score of 403 points.

Photograph of the Finnish vocalists Lasse Mårtenson, Eino Grön and Ilkka Lipsanen alias Danny.
